text: Kathrin Unterwurzacher (born 5 June 1992) is an Austrian judoka. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 63 kg event, in which she was eliminated in the repechage by Anicka van Emden of the Netherlands. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian female judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Austria Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Universiade medalists in judo Category:Universiade bronze medalists for Austria Category:European Games competitors for Austria Category:Judoka at the 2015 European Games Category:Judoka at the 2019 European Games Category:Medalists at the 2013 Summer Universiade
